\par \pard\plain \s17\sa120 \f7\fs20\lang3081 The object of the game is to discover the secret code set by the computer.
\par To learn how to use Help, press {\fs18 F1}.
\par \pard \s17\sb240\sa60 {\b The Game
\par }\pard\plain \f7\fs20\lang3081 {\uldb AutoPlace}{\v AUTOPLACE}
\par \pard\plain \s17\sb240\sa60 \f7\fs20\lang3081 {\b How to...
